tiers.ability_description: Whenever Light Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.
Whenever an enemy is defeated by a Scoundrel ally, that enemy can't be revived.
Whenever Cara Dune removes Turn Meter from an enemy, she deals damage to them equal to 25% of their Max Health.
Whenever Dark Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.
The first time each Hutt Cartel ally falls below 50% Health, all Hutt Cartel allies reduce their cooldowns by 1 and gain 10% Turn Meter.
Whenever Light Side allies grant a buff to another ally, that other ally recovers 3% Health and Protection.
Whenever a Scoundrel ally deals damage to an enemy and no other enemy is Ability Blocked, inflict Ability Block for 1 turn on the enemy, which can't be evaded or resisted.
Whenever Light Side allies grant a buff to another ally, that other ally recovers 3% Health and Protection.
Dark Side allies recover 2% Health whenever they critically hit an enemy.
Whenever Light Side allies inflict a debuff on an enemy, they deal damage to that enemy equal to 2% of that enemy's Max Health.
Whenever Rebel Fighter allies lose a stack of Heal Over Time, they gain a stack of Heal Over Time (10%) for 2 turns.
At the beginning of their turn, Dark Side allies have +25% chance to dispel all Debuffs on themself.
Whenever Empire allies target another ally with an ability during their turn, they both gain 5% Defense, Max Health, Max Protection, and Offense (stacking) until the end of battle.
Whenever Light Side allies inflict a debuff on an enemy, they deal damage to that enemy equal to 2% of that enemy's Max Health.
Whenever an enemy is defeated by a Mandalorian ally, that enemy can't be revived.
The first time each Light Side ally reaches 75%, 50%, and 25% Health grant them Protection Up (50%) for 2 turns, which can't be dispelled or prevented.
